{"tid":802710,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[唔志在果幾億] IU十周年見面會「分級」票價超佛心","createTime":"2018-09-01T15:56:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-02T10:15:59.000Z","uid":34643,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"30d44c48b4dc9e33b85585949491718f3ba87da1","tid":802710,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T15:56:15.000Z","msg":"本月 18 日就是 IU 出道滿十周年的日子了，陪著許多人長大乘家、也陪著許多人邁入青春的她，今年當然也會依約和粉絲相見羅！<br />\n<br />\n從 IU 出道就合作至今的經紀公司 Kakao M 本周宣布：「IU 將於 9 月 15 日傍晚在首爾的環球藝術中心，舉行出道十周年紀念粉絲見面會《IU+》。」並公開了兩個版本的預告海報。<br />\n<br />\n特別的是，粉絲群遍布男女老少的 IU 這次特別安排兩個場次，第一場是專屬於 10 代 UAENA 的 &ldquo;Talk to I10U&rdquo;，第二場則是限定 2000 年 2 月 29 日後出生的 UAENA 才能參加的 &ldquo;Invitat10n&rdquo;，創意十足的命名和企劃讓人十分期待，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><ins><em>全場 35000 韓元（約合台幣 969 元）的票價</em></ins></strong></span></span>也讓粉絲在大呼佛心之余也害怕搶票難度更高。<br />\n<br />\n下個月 4 日晚間八點就鞥上 MelOn Ticket 預購《IU+》的門票，先祝 UAENA 們搶票成功羅！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.y3600.com/d/file/p/2018/09/01/23e4969ec7859bc1b83ff6ed5af0321b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.y3600.com%2Fd%2Ffile%2Fp%2F2018%2F09%2F01%2F23e4969ec7859bc1b83ff6ed5af0321b.jpg&h=ea332348&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.y3600.com/d/file/p/2018/09/01/633e90fcc2eeb3e3d1767d6de194511f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.y3600.com%2Fd%2Ffile%2Fp%2F2018%2F09%2F01%2F633e90fcc2eeb3e3d1767d6de194511f.jpg&h=5e1519ec&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dba1105f171881553b33fbdde06b8d56c06b0f85","tid":802710,"uid":66154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T16:18:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a33e5cb875c5e8e3aa840dc5f23883f57b3f7488","tid":802710,"uid":36359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T16:25:30.000Z","msg":"第一場仲平 25000圜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"233